<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alternative Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/alternatives.css">
</head>
<body>
    

    <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>



    <section class="alternative">
  <div class="alternative-content">

    

    <h1>
      Nature's <br />
      <span><i>Synthesis.</i></span>
    </h1>

    <p><b>
      Transitioning to a non-toxic lifestyle requires molecular precision.
      Discover simple, effective, and natural replacements for hazardous
      everyday products.</b>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="care-section">

    <div class="care-header">
    <div class="icon-box">💧</div>
    <div>
      <h2>Skin & Personal Care</h2>
      <p><b>SWAP PROTOCOL 1</b></p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- CARD 1 -->
  <details class="care-card">
    <summary class="card-header">

      <div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="risk"><b>DIAGNOSTIC RISK</b></span>
          <span class="desc"><b>HARSH FACE WASHES (SLS & PARABENS)</b></span>
        </div>

        <div class="swap">
          <span class="safe"><b>BIO-SAFE SWAP</b></span>
          <h3>GRAM FLOUR (BESAN) + TURMERIC + RAW MILK</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow">⌄</div>

    </summary>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="title"><b>SCIENTIFIC RATIONALE</b></p>
      <p class="content">
        Besan gently exfoliates without stripping natural oils. Turmeric provides
        antibacterial properties while raw milk maintains skin pH balance.
      </p>

      <div class="extra">
        <span class="prep"><b>2 MINS PREP</b></span>
        <span class="price"><b>₹ - AFFORDABLE</b></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <!-- CARD 2 -->
  <details class="care-card">
    <summary class="card-header">

      <div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="risk"><b>DIAGNOSTIC RISK</b></span>
          <span class="desc"><b>CHEMICAL SUNSCREENS (OXYBENZONE)</b></span>
        </div>

        <div class="swap">
          <span class="safe"><b>BIO-SAFE SWAP</b></span>
          <h3>ZINC OXIDE MINERAL SUNSCREEN</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow">⌄</div>

    </summary>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="title"><b>SCIENTIFIC RATIONALE</b></p>
      <p class="content">
        Mineral screens provide a physical UV barrier, preventing bloodstream absorption
        of endocrine disruptors like Oxybenzone.
        
      </p>

      <div class="extra">
        <span class="prep"><b>READY PREP</b></span>
        <span class="price"><b>₹ - MODERATE</b></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>


  <!-- card 3 -->


   <details class="care-card">
    <summary class="card-header">

      <div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="risk"><b>DIAGNOSTIC RISK</b></span>
          <span class="desc"><b>COMMERCIAL MOISTURIZERS (MINERAL OIL)</b></span>
        </div>

        <div class="swap">
          <span class="safe"><b>BIO-SAFE SWAP</b></span>
          <h3>PURE AELO VERA OR JOJOBA OIL</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow">⌄</div>

    </summary>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="title"><b>SCIENTIFIC RATIONALE</b></p>
      <p class="content">
        Jojoba oil is molecularly identical to human sebum, providing deep hydration
         without the pore-clogging effects of petroleum-derived mineral oils.
      </p>

      <div class="extra">
        <span class="prep"><b>READY PREP</b></span>
        <span class="price"><b>₹ - MODERATE</b></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>


  <div class="care-header">
    <div class="icon-box">✨</div>
    <div>
      <h2>Household Cleaners</h2>
      <p><b>SWAP PROTOCOL 2</b></p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- card 1 -->


   <details class="care-card">
    <summary class="card-header">

      <div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="risk"><b>DIAGNOSTIC RISK</b></span>
          <span class="desc"><b>TOXIC FLOOR CLEANERS (AMMONIA, BLEACH)</b></span>
        </div>

        <div class="swap">
          <span class="safe"><b>BIO-SAFE SWAP</b></span>
          <h3>WHITE VINEGAR + WATER + LEMON OIL</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow">⌄</div>

    </summary>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="title"><b>SCIENTIFIC RATIONALE</b></p>
      <p class="content">
        Acetic acid in vinegar effectively neutralizes common household pathogens without releasing
         the Volatile Organic Compounds (VOCs) found in bleach-based cleaners.
      </p>

      <div class="extra">
        <span class="prep"><b>1 MIN PREP</b></span>
        <span class="price"><b>₹ - AFFORDABLE</b></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>


  <!-- card 2 -->


   <details class="care-card">
    <summary class="card-header">

      <div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="risk"><b>DIAGNOSTIC RISK</b></span>
          <span class="desc"><b>SYNTHETICAIR FRESHNERS (VOCs/PHTHALATES)</b></span>
        </div>

        <div class="swap">
          <span class="safe"><b>BIO-SAFE SWAP</b></span>
          <h3>SIMMER POT (CINNAMON, CITRUS, CLOVES)</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow">⌄</div>

    </summary>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="title"><b>SCIENTIFIC RATIONALE</b></p>
      <p class="content">
        Boiling spices releases nature's aromatic compounds directly, avoiding
         the phthalates legally hidden under 'fragrance' loopholes in plug-in fresheners.
      </p>

      <div class="extra">
        <span class="prep"><b>10 MINS PREP</b></span>
        <span class="price"><b>₹ - AFFORDABLE</b></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>




  <div class="care-header">
    <div class="icon-box">🍎</div>
    <div>
      <h2>Food & Diet</h2>
      <p><b>SWAP PROTOCOL 3</b></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- card 1 -->


   <details class="care-card">
    <summary class="card-header">

      <div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="risk"><b>DIAGNOSTIC RISK</b></span>
          <span class="desc"><b>REFINED SUGAR & ASPARTAME</b></span>
        </div>

        <div class="swap">
          <span class="safe"><b>BIO-SAFE SWAP</b></span>
          <h3>JAGGERY (GUD) OR STEVIA LEAVES</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow">⌄</div>

    </summary>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="title"><b>SCIENTIFIC RATIONALE</b></p>
      <p class="content">
        Refined sugar triggers acute insulin spikes and inflammatory responses.
         Stevia is a zero-glycemic index plant extract with no metabolic disruption.

      </p>

      <div class="extra">
        <span class="prep"><b>READY PREP</b></span>
        <span class="price"><b>₹ - MODERATE</b></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>


  <!-- card 2 -->


   <details class="care-card">
    <summary class="card-header">

      <div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="risk"><b>DIAGNOSTIC RISK</b></span>
          <span class="desc"><b>PROCESSED SNACKS (TRANS FAT, TBHQ)</b></span>
        </div>

        <div class="swap">
          <span class="safe"><b>BIO-SAFE SWAP</b></span>
          <h3>ROASTED MAKHANA OR NATIVE NUTS</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="arrow">⌄</div>

    </summary>

    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="title"><b>SCIENTIFIC RATIONALE</b></p>
      <p class="content">
        Native snacks are rich in magnesium and protein, avoiding the 
        petroleum-based preservatives (TBHQ) and trans fats found in processed chips.

      </p>

      <div class="extra">
        <span class="prep"><b>5 MINS PREP</b></span>
        <span class="price"><b>₹ - MODERATE</b></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>

</section>


<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-container">

    <div class="cta-text">
      <h2>
        Incremental <span><i>Transformation.</i></span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <b>Personal health optimization is an iterative process. Select one high-usage product
        and implement a bio-safe swap this week.</b>
      </p>
    </div>

    <button class="cta-btn" id="scanBtn">
      Initialize Scan Engine →
    </button>

    <script>
  document.getElementById("scanBtn").addEventListener("click", function() {
    window.location.href = "/";
  });
</script>

  </div>
</section>
   <%- include('partials/footer') %> 
</body>
</html>